    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS timing. This driver-spec example is paired with a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including professional rear subframe reinforcement and documented rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the legendary E46 handling dynamics are preserved. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain is exceptionally responsive and pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key performance icon for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
