    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This exceptionally well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, showing only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful, low-mileage ownership. Step inside to a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of significant wear. All onboard technology\u2014from the responsive touchscreen infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has been strictly serviced according to the manufacturer's schedule, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly, providing a smooth, confident ride that feels tight and responsive on the road. This is a reliable, high-quality vehicle perfect for someone who wants the peace of mind that comes with a documented history of prideful ownership.",
      "price": 34900.0,
